    • releaseCollection

      R<RpcStatus> releaseCollection(ReleaseCollectionParam requestParam)
      Releases the loaded collection from memory. All data in the released collection remains intact after this operation. You can load the collection back to memory again using loadCollection().
      参数:
      requestParam - A LoadCollectionParam object as the request parameter.
      返回:
      A RpcStatus object indicating whether this operation succeeds.

      R<FlushResponse> flush(FlushParam requestParam)
      Seals all entities in the specified collection. Any insertion after a flush operation results in generating new segments. Only sealed segments can be indexed.
      参数:
      requestParam - A FlushParam object as the request parameter.
      返回:
      A FlushResponse object that offers methods to get information about the flush operation.
